### Submit a leave request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/leave-requests
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
    "LeaveTypeId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
    "StartDate": "2026-05-18",
    "EndDate": "2026-05-20",
    "Reason": "Family trip"
}

### Get my leave requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leave-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get a leave request by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leave-requests/{44f9a9ba-4ce4-41ba-a21f-19359d419cb8}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Approve or reject a leave request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/leave-requests/{44f9a9ba-4ce4-41ba-a21f-19359d419cb8}/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
    "Action": "APPROVED",
    "Remarks": "Approved for travel"
}

### Cancel a leave request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/leave-requests/{44f9a9ba-4ce4-41ba-a21f-19359d419cb8}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get my leave balances
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leave-balances?year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get a user's leave balances
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leave-balances/users/{232ff34e-5bde-4417-a37c-87e62a2bd948}?year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Assign leave balances for a year
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/leave-balances/assign?year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

